snippet.title: The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt - Next Gen Update Trailer | The Game Awards 2022
snippet.description: The long-awaited PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X|S, and PC next-gun update for The Witcher 3 is almost here. Check out a brand new trailer showing some of things you can expect when The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt updates for free on December 14.
